column7:
Enter the task start date in the following format:
'mm/dd/yyyy' for one time workflows
'#' for weekly workflows (where # represents day of the week & Monday = day 1)
'dd' for monthly workflows
'mmm/mmm/mmm/mmm dd' for monthly workflows e.g. feb/may/aug/nov 17
'mm/dd' for yearly workflows
column8:

'dd' for monthly workflows
'mmm/mmm/mmm/mmm dd' for monthly workflows e.g. feb/may/aug/nov 17
'mm/dd' for yearly workflows
